title: Google\Cloud\Dlp\V2\PartitionId
name: PartitionId
description:
Datastore partition ID.

A partition ID identifies a grouping of entities. The grouping is always by project and namespace, however the namespace ID may be empty. A partition ID contains several dimensions: project ID and namespace ID.

Generated from protobuf message google.privacy.dlp.v2.PartitionId
